B.ai9=new A.e("Black played G-3i, anticipating a Rook exchange. Then he moved the Gold onto 4i, thereby strengthening his defense. There followed a flamboyant show of exchanging both Rooks and Bishops (Diagram 2). The position is well-balanced, but take note that Black's camp allows no space for a Rook drop.")
B.Oi=new A.q("ln1g4l/1ks6/3p2n2/ppps2g1p/4P1pp1/P2S1p2P/1PPP5/2KG2S2/LN3G1NL b RB2Prb2p","Diagram 2")
B.ajd=new A.e("Below is another example in which the maxim in question was put to good use. Unlike above, this is a joseki position in the central Rook against static Rook opening.")
