B.an2=new A.e("From Diagram 6, Black's K-7h won't do. G*7i will end the game.")
B.aio=new A.e("Back in Diagram 5, there is one move you can play to get yourself out of danger, which is...?")
B.Vp=A.a(s(["G6g-6h"]),t.s)
B.aaZ=new A.Q(null,B.Vp,B.u)
B.agZ=new A.e("By placing two Golds side by side to guard your King, you can buy time. In the yagura-opening, you are supposed to place your Gold on 6g, but when you get into the endgame, the Gold had better be on 6h for the defense.")
B.aie=new A.e("I might add that S-6h instead of G6g-6h is less preferable, even if it may appear to be similar in effect. There is a well-known endgame tesuji against the Yagura: S*6i, to which S-6h is hardly well-prepared.")
B.aoe=new A.e("Just remember that a Gold functions better when sitting in the back rank.")
