B.af9=new A.e('Black, with the static Rook, is setting up for a quick attack. White, on the other hand, has formed a Mino-castle with two Golds and a Silver. Black will then play S4f, reinforcing his attack. This may seem at odds with "three generals\' defence," but in this case the Silver on 4h is regarded as part of the defence.\n')
