B.aop=new A.e("Diagram 1-2 (up to S-7h) shows the beginning of a slow game, where the static Rook side has built up the left Mino-castle, vying with White's sturdy guard.")
B.ak2=new A.e("In a ranging-against-static-Rook game, the right half of the board (where the Rooks sit) is likely to become the battlefield, rather than making direct attack against each King.")
