B.akG=new A.e("White in Diagram 3-4 (up to N2e) has built the Mino-castle. However, as far as the double-ranging-Rook is concerned, the Mino is not a very good defence. Incidentally, Black's King is not very safe, either, with his vulnerable right edge.")
